            <div class='content-div'>
                <div class='content-div__title'>
                    Input Elements
                </div>
                <div class='content-div__content'>

                    <h2>Introduction</h2>
                    <p>Define input variables in the styles/_variables.scss file.</p>

                    <p>Inputs' styles are completely reset by {{globals.githubStylesNormalizeLink}} and {{globals.githubStylesResetLink}}.</p>
                    <p>Input styling variables are defined in the {{globals.githubStylesVariablesLink}} file and applied in the {{globals.githubStylesInputsLink}} file.</p>
                    <p>Customize your buttons by first editing the variables in styles/_variables.scss and then editing inputs.scss for fine grained control.</p>
                    <p>Below is how each element looks with the current style definitions.</p>

                    <h2 class='mt40'>Default Input</h2>
                    {{show-code code="{{input placeholder='Text input ...'}}"}}
                    <h3>Result</h3>
                    <p>{{input placeholder='Text input ...'}}</p>

                    <h2 class='mt40'>Medium Width</h2>
                    {{show-code code="{{input class='input--med-width' placeholder='Text input ...'}}"}}
                    <h3>Result</h3>
                    <p>{{input class='input--med-width' placeholder='Text input ...'}}</p>

                    <h2 class='mt40'>Small Width</h2>
                    {{show-code code="{{input class='input--small-width' placeholder='Input..'}}"}}
                    <h3>Result</h3>
                    <p>{{input class='input--small-width' placeholder='Input..'}}</p>

                    <h2 class='mt40'>Disabled</h2>
                    {{show-code code="{{input disabled=true placeholder='Disabled ...'}}"}}
                    <h3>Result</h3>
                    <p>{{input disabled=true placeholder='Disabled ...'}}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

